article.description: Yoeli Childs had 29 points and 13 rebounds as BYU beat San Diego 87-73 on Saturday night. TJ Haws added 26 points for the Cougars.
article.headline: Childs carries BYU over San Diego 87-73
article.linkText: Childs carries BYU over San Diego 87-73
article.story: PROVO, Utah -- Yoeli Childs had 29 points and 13 rebounds as BYU beat San Diego 87-73 on Saturday night. TJ Haws added 26 points for the Cougars. Nick Emery had 15 points for BYU (19-12, 11-5 West Coast Conference). Zac Seljaas added 10 points. Isaiah Wright had 19 points and seven rebounds for the Toreros (18-13, 7-9). Olin Carter III added 15 points. Tyler Williams had 11 points. The Cougars improve to 2-0 against the Toreros for the season. BYU defeated San Diego 88-82 on Feb. 14. The Cougars and the Toreros next take the floor in the West Coast Conference Tournament. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
